thread.title: Naseem

author: Naseem
title: Naseem
text: I chose Crewe because I saw that the app had won awards and I'm not tech savvy so wanted something that made it easy to create my own photobook. The app is great, I found it really easy to use and the finished photobook was delivered on time and well packaged. It was a gift for my cousin and she loved it so much it brought her to tears. Some of the photos hadn't come out as cleanly as I would like (there was a little colour bleeding) but it was reasonably good quality overall and I'm very happy with it
